Company Overview of Aly Energy Services, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Aly Energy Services, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides various oilfield services to owners and operators of oil and gas wells in the United States. It offers equipment, such as centrifuges and auxiliary solids control equipment, mud circulating tanks and auxiliary equipment, portable mud mixing plants, containment systems, centrifuges and auxiliary solids control equipment, and measurement-while-drilling kits primarily for land-based horizontal drilling applications. It also engages in the hauling of rental equipment to the well site and rig-up/rig-down, as well as provides personnel at the customer’s well site to operate the equipment. The company serves clients primarily in the Perm...
Aly Energy Services, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides various oilfield services to owners and operators of oil and gas wells in the United States. It offers equipment, such as centrifuges and auxiliary solids control equipment, mud circulating tanks and auxiliary equipment, portable mud mixing plants, containment systems, centrifuges and auxiliary solids control equipment, and measurement-while-drilling kits primarily for land-based horizontal drilling applications. It also engages in the hauling of rental equipment to the well site and rig-up/rig-down, as well as provides personnel at the customer’s well site to operate the equipment. The company serves clients primarily in the Permian Basin, Eagle Ford Shale, Utica Shale, Marcellus Shale, Woodford Shale, Granite Wash, Mississippian Lime, and Tuscaloosa Marine Shale. Aly Energy Services, Inc. was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Houston, Texas.
