ABOUT ALY ENERGY SERVICES


            
  Aly Energy Services, Inc. is an oilfield manufacturing, rental and services company driven by fast-growing horizontal drilling activity in the North American shale plays. Headquartered in Houston, we service a growing number of oil and gas companies in every major North American Shale Play, and are pursuing acquisition opportunities to broaden our services and regional reach.    








Our Milestones




 2001-2011 
  

  Chairman & CEO President Micki Hidayatallah founded Allis-Chalmers Energy Inc. In 2008 Fortune named Allis Chalmers as the 3rd fastest growing company in the USA ranking #1 in revenue growth. Allis-Chalmers sold for $1.1 billion in 2011. 

 JULY 2012 
  

  Aly Energy is founded by Micki Hidayatallah. 

 OCTOBER 2012 
  

  Aly Energy acquires Austin Chalk Petroleum Services Corp. (ACPS) 

 April 2014 
  

Acquired United Centrifuge USA


 July 2014 
  

Acquired Evolution Guidance Systems 


 August 2014 
  

  Equipment Acquisition from United Centrifuge Ltd. Saskatchewan Canada 


 





MISSION STATEMENT


            
  To create a multi-faceted oilfield services company, through both organic growth and acquisitions, that provides its customers the best in class operators and highest quality equipment in a cost effective manner while maintaining the highest safety standards.    










